&lt;p&gt;The patch makes sure that we stop taking the segments into account as soon as we reach the first segment managed by the &lt;tt&gt;CommitLogSegmentManager&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15286641" author="blerer" created="Tue, 17 May 2016 13:45:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=blambov&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;blambov&quot;&gt;blambov&lt;/a&gt; could you review?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15286833" author="blambov" created="Tue, 17 May 2016 15:25:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This has been fixed so many times I&apos;m not sure a solution based on checking the managed list could work at all.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;An easier solution is to use &lt;tt&gt;CommitLogSegment.idBase&lt;/tt&gt; as a threshold: replay only if segment id is below that. This is done in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-10202&quot; title=&quot;simplify CommitLogSegmentManager&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-10202&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-10202&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, which only targets trunk &amp;#8211; I think it&apos;s best to take the code from there (&lt;tt&gt;CommitLogSegment&lt;/tt&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/compare/trunk...blambov:10202-commitlog#diff-7720d4b5123a354876e0b3139222f34eR63&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;&lt;tt&gt;replayLimitId&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;shouldReplay&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;resetReplayLimit&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;CommitLog&lt;/tt&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/compare/trunk...blambov:10202-commitlog#diff-05c1e4fd86fea19b8e0552b1f289be85L133&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;&lt;tt&gt;recover&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/compare/trunk...blambov:10202-commitlog#diff-05c1e4fd86fea19b8e0552b1f289be85R427&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;&lt;tt&gt;stopUnsafe&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/a&gt;) and backport it.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Do we need to go back all the way to 2.1?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
